-- Malaga Law Solicitors - Malaga/Mijas
('Malaga Law Solicitors', 'Legal', 'Boutique English-styled law firm with principal office in Malaga and liaison office in London. Managed by Paloma España, one of only a handful of dual-qualified solicitors in Spain entitled to practice as both a Spanish lawyer (Abogada) and English solicitor (Solicitor of the Supreme Court of England & Wales). Provides comprehensive legal services to English-speaking expats and international clients throughout Spain. Specializes in property law and conveyancing, family law and divorce, wills and probate, power of attorney, NIE applications, and general legal advice. Deep understanding of both Spanish and UK legal systems with personalized service and clear communication in English throughout the legal process. Serves clients throughout Costa del Sol, Andalucía, and nationwide including Mijas, Fuengirola, Marbella, Benalmádena, and surrounding areas.', 'Boulevard de la Cala, s/n, 29649', 'Mijas', 'Málaga', '+34 952 494 996', NULL, 'https://www.malagalaw.com/', true, false, false, false, NOW(), NOW());
